									Pago con QR
								</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-0.5">
									Escanea, ordena y paga
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<svg
							class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-[--color-avoqado-green] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all flex-shrink-0"
							fill="none"
